n the last decade selling over 60 million units thanks to its adaptability and hackability. And on scores of those computers is Annandale’s beautiful travel photos which he shoots all across the world.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774297\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774297\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original.webp\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-800x420.webp\" alt=\"A bustling train station with people walking in different directions. The ceiling is arched with a metallic design. Signs and digital screens are displayed overhead, and workers in orange vests are visible among the travelers.\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-800x420.webp 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-320x168.webp 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-150x79.webp 150w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-300x157.webp 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-400x209.webp 400w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original-550x288.webp 550w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/original.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774297\"\u003eAnnandale glimpes his image at Auckland’s Britomart train station in 2019.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774278\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774278\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A hot air balloon floats over the lush, ancient landscape of Bagan, Myanmar, with numerous temples and pagodas scattered across the greenery, silhouetted against a misty morning backdrop with mountains in the distance.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/balloon.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774278\"\u003e‘Balloon’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774283\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774283\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-800x536.jpg\" alt=\"A fisherman stands on a bamboo raft on a calm river at dusk. He holds a pole and is accompanied by cormorants. A lantern hangs from the raft, casting a warm glow. Misty karst mountains rise in the background, creating a serene and mysterious atmosphere.\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-800x536.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-1536x1028.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/fisherman.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774283\"\u003e‘Fisherman’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"a