u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774290\"\u003e‘Sand’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774277\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774277\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"The image shows the Northern Lights, with green and purple hues, illuminating the night sky over a mountainous landscape and a calm body of water. Snow partially covers the ground.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/aurora.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774277\"\u003e‘Aurora’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774293\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774293\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A serene waterfall cascades over dark, rocky ledges covered with patches of green moss and grass. The water appears silky and smooth, and surrounding foliage hints at an autumn setting with hints of yellow and brown.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/waterfall.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774293\"\u003e‘Waterfall’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774280\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774280\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A scenic view of the Grand Canyon under a partly cloudy sky. A leafless tree stands prominently in the foreground, adjacent to rocky terrain, with expansive canyon vistas and shadows cast by clouds in the background.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/canyon.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774280\"\u003e‘Canyon’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cp\u003eWhen it comes to iconic desktop pictures, nothing competes with \u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/2017/11/20/photographer-behind-windows-xp-bliss-shot-3-new-phone-wallpapers/\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eMicrosoft Windows XP \u003cem\u003eBliss\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e taken by Charles O’Rear which is widely considered the most viewed photo in the world. However, Raspberry Pis are often used in educational settings and \u003ca href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5YfJWYELA3k\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ein YouTube videos\u003c/a\u003e that have millions of views. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“It always feels special to see any of the photos in these situations,” says Annandale, who is from the U.K. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“I don’t think that will ever get old, and it’s always exciting to see them in use out in the wild, a particular favourite being spotting a Raspberry Pi-powered information screen (displaying the Iceland “road” image) whilst travelling through Auckland’s Britomart train station in 2019.” \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe Iceland photo Annandale mentions is probably the best-known Raspperry Pi desktop image as it was the first photo wallpaper and launched with a major upgrade of the operating system (OS). \u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774285\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774285\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A dramatic sunset over a body of water with silhouetted mountain peaks. The sun breaks through thick clouds, casting golden rays across the sky and reflecting on the waves below.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/islands.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774285\"\u003e‘Islands’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774291\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774291\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A breathtaking sunset over an ancient temple landscape, silhouetting the pagodas against a golden sky. Dense greenery surrounds the temples, with rolling hills in the background under a warm, glowing horizon.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/temple.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774291\"\u003e‘Temple’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774286\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774286\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Night view of Marina Bay Sands in Singapore, illuminated by green laser lights, with its three towers and sky park. The ArtScience Museum, shaped like a lotus, and surrounding buildings are lit with red lighting, reflecting on the water.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/lasers.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774286\"\u003e‘Lasers’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774281\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774281\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A scenic view of a lighthouse perched on a grassy cliff overlooking the ocean. The rugged green terrain leads to a majestic, cloud-topped mountain. Fluffy clouds dot the blue sky, enhancing the breathtaking landscape.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/cliff.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774281\"\u003e‘Cliff’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003ch2\u003eTraveling Photographer\u003c/h2\u003e \u003cp\u003eAnnandale works for the Raspberry Pi Foundation, an educational charity distinct from Raspberry Pi the commercial entity. He works in software engineering, building educational programs for young people. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eIt means he is only a part-time photographer but when he does work he often travels for a substantial amount of time. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“Since around 2012 I’ve been shooting travel, landscape and expedition images at some level,” he explains. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e“More recently, whilst travel time has reduced significantly, I’ve focused more on purposeful image-taking for science and documentary use (this has led to a fellowship at the Royal Geographical Society).”\u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774287\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774287\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A dramatic black and white photograph of a rugged, snow-covered mountain peak partially obscured by swirling clouds. The scene captures a sense of majesty and mystery.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/mountain.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774287\"\u003e‘Mountain’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774292\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774292\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-800x536.jpg\" alt=\"Sunbeams filter through a dense forest, illuminating the trees in a serene atmosphere. The shafts of light create a radiant, almost magical effect in the early morning or late afternoon setting.\" width=\"800\" height=\"536\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-800x536.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-1536x1029.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/trees.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774292\"\u003e‘Trees’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_774282\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-774282\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds.jpg\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A stunning sunset over a calm body of water, with dramatic orange and red clouds filling the sky. Silhouettes of distant mountains frame the horizon, creating a breathtaking landscape.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-320x214.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2024/12/clouds.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-774282\"\u003e‘Clouds’\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cp\u003eAll 16 of Annandale’s desktop images can be found on Raspberry Pi computers. For more of his work, head to his \u003ca href=\"https://www.gregannandale.com/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003ewebsite\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/greg_a/?hl=en\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/greg-a/\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003eFlickr\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e \u003chr/\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImage credits:\u003c/strong\u003e Photographs by Greg Annandale\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n          \n      \n\n              \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003ePetaPixel articles may include affiliate links; if you buy something through such a link, PetaPixel may earn a commission.\u003c/p\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \n    \n\n    \n          \n      \n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n    \n          \n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/article\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
